{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop all state benefit payments to non-British citizens",
        "additional_details": "Expenses are increasing as the cost-of-living increases. We are concerned that illegal migrants keep arriving onto British shores and are impacting our economy. We believe it is unfair and that British taxes should not be spent this way.",
        "background": "I would like the Government to cease all state benefit payments and support to people who are not British citizens.",
